---
/**
 * QUOTE REQUEST PAGE
 * ====================
 *
 * The quote form is a React island (complex multi-step form with
 * cart/line items, validation, and Firestore submission).
 *
 * MIGRATION NOTE:
 *   Extract the form logic from QuoteRequestPage.tsx into a
 *   QuoteRequestForm.tsx React component and mount with client:load.
